dc_title_s: Ensenada : plano de la ciudad = city map / by Carlos Esparza Ramón.
dc_description_s: rELIEF SHOW BY SHADING Includes inset map of downtown, index of colonias, and color advertisements. Inset maps on recto: Ampliación 1: Cibola del Mar, San Miguel -- Ampliación 2: El Sauzal de Rodríguez -- Ampliación 3: Ensenada centro -- Ampliación 4: R. Sánchez Taboada, Maneadero plano urbano -- Ensenada [coastal area]. On verso: Ensenada [coastal area] -- Ruta del vino = Wine Country -- Las Cañada campamento, Ensenada Baja California, Méx. Relevant tourist resorts are shown pictorially.
